snippet.title: Johnny Depp Appears At Comic-Con As Grindelwald
snippet.description:
With Johnny Depp making a surprise appearance at Comic-Con as his “Fantastic Beasts” character just after ex-wife Amber Heard promoted “Aquaman”, Carlos Bustamante and Graeme O’Neil react on "ET Canada Live".
